description: This had to be the shiest boy I have ever met in my office. At the first sight he looked very poor. To my surprise he didn´t complain, he lived in a small apartment in Prague and was happy with what he had. I think his main problem was the lack of ambition. His salary demands were very low, he didn´t think ahead at all. I had no idea how he could get by. Judging by what he said to me, he was from a bit dysfunctional family, which probably was the cause of his behavior. His shyness started to be annoying so I shifted our conversation to more interesting topic. He was very young and frightened, perhaps that was why he was willing to do all my favorite things for such a low price. And I couldn´t wait to see this cutie swallow my hot cum.
title: Dirty Scout 51
